[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     G --> M
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     M -->|Per-unit forecasts<br/>+ intervals| N[DynamoDB<br/>census-forecasts]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     M -->|Sample trajectories| O[S3 Bucket<br/>forecast-samples/]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     N -->|Query| P[Bed Huddle Dashboard /<br/>Transfer Center /<br/>OR Scheduler /<br/>ED Diversion Tool]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     R[EventBridge Schedule<br/>weekly + monthly] -->|Trigger| S[Step Functions<br/>retraining-pipeline]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     S -->|Train| T[SageMaker Training Jobs]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     T -->|New models| J
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     T -->|New models| K
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     T -->|New models| L
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     I -->|Errors / metrics| Z[CloudWatch<br/>Alarms + SNS DLQ]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     style B fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     style M fill:#9f9,stroke:#333
